flowchart LR
  %% Pocket "Missing Information" training/eval flow (example scenario)

  A["Raw tech pack PDF/Excel"] --> B["Extract pages + text + tables + OCR"]
  B --> C["Normalize into schema<br/>sections, measurements, BOM, construction notes"]

  C --> D["Pocket Checklist\n(ground truth rubric)"]
  D --> D1["Pocket presence\n(does garment have pocket?)"]
  D --> D2["Pocket type\n(patch, welt, flap, kangaroo, etc)"]
  D --> D3["Count + placement\n(L/R, chest, side seam)"]
  D --> D4["Dimensions + tolerances\n(width/height, opening)"]
  D --> D5["Construction details\nstitch, reinforcement, closure"]
  D --> D6["Visual reference\ndiagram/placement callout"]

  C --> E["Label findings\nMissing / inconsistent / contradictory"]
  E --> F["Attach evidence\npageNumber + snippet + bbox highlight"]

  F --> G["Gold set (reviewed)\n+ hard negatives"]
  G --> H["Offline eval\nRecall@Pocket + Precision\nHighlight IoU\nPage accuracy"]
  H --> I["MLflow run\nmetrics + artifacts"]

